  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſi/ tawa Peſtifschana nahk/ johs/ bet neweens bija/ kas manni\nredſi/ winna Alga irr pee win-\nna/ un winna Atmaſſifschana usturretu/ tapehz palihdſeja unar\nirr winna Breekſcha."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "nans Efkins/ un nanna Bahri\nſiba irr mann usturrejſi."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee nosauſs winnus\ntohs ſwehtus Laudis/ tohs At-\npeſtitus ta KUNGA/ un tu tap-\nſi nosauſta ta Peemekleta/ tas\nne-atſtahte Pilſſahts."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht eſmu es tohs Lau-\ndis faminnis mannā Dufmibā-\nun tohs peedſirdinajs mann\nBahriſbā/ un winno Speh-\npee Semmes nomettis."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta LXIII. Nodalla.\nTa Praueeta Aprakſifschana tahs Uswarrescha-\nnas Preczas/ un tahs Uswarrefchanas Leel-\nKunga no Eedoma/ tas irr Kristus/ prett wiſ-\nfeem faweem Eenaidneeekeem : 1. etc.\nAs irr tas/ kas no Ee-\nEdoma nahk/ ar aptlazzi-\ntahn Drehbehm no\nBozras/ tas/ kas ta irr iſgres-\nchts tawa Apgehrbā/ kas ap-\nkahrt ect eekſch fawa leela Speh-\nka? Es/ kas es Taifnibu runna-\nju/ un warrens eſmu atpeſtiht."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta LXIV. Nodalla.\nWeena ſirdiga Luugſchana to Judo Kauech-\nka Deews tohs atkah gribbetu ſchehloht :\nNo augſtas Debbes noſkatitees/ un Krif-\nto Peſtitaju fuhtiht : 1. etc.\nS mahzifschu peemin-\nneht ta KUNG-\nSchehlaſtibu/ta KUN-\nGA teizainu Slawn/pahr wiſſi-\nko tas KUNGS mums irr pa-\nrahdijs/ un to leelu Labbuim-\npee Ifraēta Namna/ ko winſo-\nteem parahdijs irr pehz farwah-\nApschehtſchanahm/ un pehz fa-\nwas leelas Schehlaſtivas."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rapehz irr tad taws Ap-\ngehrbs tik tarſaus/ un taws\nDrehbes ka weena Wihna-Spai-\nda-Minneja?"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es eſmu to Spaidu tweens\npats minnis/ un neweens no\nteein Landim bija ar mannim.\nUn es eſmu tohs minnis mannā\nDufmibā/ un faminnis mannā\nBahriſbā: Tad irr winnu Stip-\nrums us mannahm Drehbehm\nHazzihts/ un es eſmu wiſſu fa-\nwu Apgehrbu ſagahnijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta Deena mannas At-\nreepſchanas irr mannā Sirāi/\nun tas Gads mannas Atpeſti-\nschanas irr nahzis."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es ſkattijobs/ un Pa-\nlīga ne bija/ un es iſtruhzina-"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiſſch fazzija: Tee i-\ntomehr manni Laudis/ Behrni-\nkas wiltigi ne buhs/ un wiſſo-\ntappe teem par Peſtitaju."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eekſch wiſſahm wiſſa-\nBehdahin tappe wiſſch opbehdi-\nnahts/ un tas Engelis wiſſa-\nWaiga irr tohs iſglahbis. Ja-\nfawu Mihleſtibu/ un zaar fan-\nSchehlaſtibu irr wiſſch tohs a-\npeſtijs. Un wiſſch uſjeſme toh-\nun netſe tohs no wezzeem La-\nkeem allachin."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tee turrejahs prett-\nun apkattinaja winna Sweh-\nGarru/ tapehz irr wiſſch tee-\npar Eenaidneeku pahrwehrtijee-\nwiſſa"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
